whole_object: As the bus wheeled around the corner, it seemed to be saying, "I'm tire-d of going in circles all day!"
single_object:
- Bus: "Why did the bus break up with its girlfriend? It just couldn't handle the emotional baggage!"
- Bicycle: "I told my bicycle a joke, but it just couldn't handle the wheel of laughter!"
- Trash can: "I asked the trash can for advice, but it just said, 'Don't throw your dreams away!'"
- Building: "This building has so many stories, it should start a podcast!"
- Flower basket: "Why did the flower basket get promoted? It always knew how to bloom where it was planted!"
